msgid "Welcome to Duka Mwecheche!"
msgstr "Mwaĩngĩrĩrwo Duka Mwecheche!"

msgid "This quick tutorial will guide you through the key features of your dashboard. You can always replay it from the menu under your username."
msgstr "Mwongozo ũno mũkuvi nĩũkũlongea kwenye maũndũ ma mũsingi ma dashibodi yaku. Nĩwĩka kũwutala tena ihinda o na rĩngĩ kuuma menu ya nthĩ ya jina rĩaku ria mtumiaji."

msgid "Your Dashboard"
msgstr "Dashibodi Yaku"

msgid "Your <strong>Supplier Dashboard</strong> shows key stats: active clients, pending bids, won bids, and open procurement requests."
msgstr "<strong>Dashibodi ya Msambazaji</strong> yaku nĩyonesya takwimu sya mũsingi: ateja matũũlũ, zabuni syĩkethĩte, zabuni syawoni, na maombi ma ununuzi matwĩkĩte."

msgid "Click <strong>Browse Requests</strong> to find procurement opportunities from businesses. Submit competitive bids to win supply contracts."
msgstr "Finya <strong>Tala Maombi</strong> nĩguo unenge fursa sya ununuzi kuuma kwa biashara. Tũma zabuni sya usindani nĩguo uwone mikataba ya usambazaji."

msgid "Track Your Bids"
msgstr "Lungamya Zabuni Syaku"

msgid "Under <strong>My Bids</strong>, monitor the status of all your bid submissions — pending, awarded, or rejected."
msgstr "Nthĩinĩ wa <strong>Zabuni Syakwa</strong>, lungamya hali ya zabuni syaku syonthe syatũmĩte — syĩkethĩte, syawĩwe, kana syakanĩtwe."

msgid "Connect with Businesses"
msgstr "Ungana na Biashara"

msgid "Use <strong>Browse Businesses</strong> to discover potential clients. Apply to become their approved supplier."
msgstr "Tumia <strong>Tala Biashara</strong> kũnenga ateja ala makethĩwa. Omba wĩ msambazaji wao mũtĩkĩtwe."

msgid "Client Relationships"
msgstr "Ũsiano wa Ateja"

msgid "Once approved, view your client list under <strong>My Clients</strong>. Build strong relationships for repeat procurement."
msgstr "Wakĩkwĩtĩkia, tala mũkusany'o wa ateja vaku nthĩinĩ wa <strong>Ateja Makwa</strong>. Tung'a ũsiano wa nguvu nĩguo ununuzi wĩũke tena."

msgid "You're All Set!"
msgstr "Ũkwĩthĩwa Weka!"

msgid "Start browsing procurement requests to grow your supply network! Replay this tutorial from your username menu anytime."
msgstr "Ambĩa kutala maombi ma ununuzi nĩguo ũkũe mtandao waku wa usambazaji! Tala mwongozo ũno tena kuuma menu ya jina ria mtumiaji ihinda o na rĩngĩ."

msgid "Your <strong>Rider Dashboard</strong> shows active deliveries, completed orders, and your performance score."
msgstr "<strong>Dashibodi ya Mũtumia wa Boda</strong> yaku nĩyonesya usafirishaji ũtũũlũ, oda syĩmalĩtie, na alama yaku ya utendaji."

msgid "Availability Toggle"
msgstr "Cenjia Upatikanaji"

msgid "Toggle your <strong>availability</strong> status so businesses know when you are ready to accept deliveries."
msgstr "Cenjia hali yaku ya <strong>upatikanaji</strong> nĩguo biashara syaĩve ihinda ũkwĩ valmis kũsyukua usafirishaji."

msgid "View your current delivery assignments under <strong>Active Deliveries</strong>. See customer details, location, and order amounts."
msgstr "Tala mĩvango yaku ya usafirishaji ya sũu nthĩinĩ wa <strong>Usafirishaji Ũtũũlũ</strong>. Ona maelezo ma mteja, vatũ, na kiasi kya oda."

msgid "Check <strong>Delivery History</strong> for a complete record of all your past deliveries."
msgstr "Tala <strong>Mbaĩtu ya Usafirishaji</strong> nĩguo ũone rekodi yonthe ya usafirishaji waku wa tene."

msgid "Track your total earnings and delivery count under <strong>My Earnings</strong>."
msgstr "Lungamya mapato maku mothe na idadi ya usafirishaji nthĩinĩ wa <strong>Mapato Makwa</strong>."

msgid "Stay available to receive delivery assignments! Replay this tutorial from your username menu anytime."
msgstr "Ikala ũkwatikana nĩguo ũsyukue mĩvango ya usafirishaji! Tala mwongozo ũno tena kuuma menu ya jina ria mtumiaji ihinda o na rĩngĩ."

